{"tid":1463970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有文宣同我入嚟！ 機場要雙贏我地要做M男！","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:25.000Z","uid":50791,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e974bb58b77e93c6c8e2e4e35393ab5f6f1babbf","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"呢兩日機場𣎴合作運動雖然成功搞到經濟，但無可否認係有失民意，縱觀兩日運動情況<br />\n<br />\n尋日係人多，但大叫廣東話令遊客好難明白發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日就唔洗講，唔夠人唯有塞路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事實上國際支持都好重要，機場除咗經濟問題，暫時其實仲有另一個天大優勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目前為止唯一一個可以比示威者唔受傷地表達訴求嘅地方！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅係打M男同情牌，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔想阻到你，但香港人已經流了太多血，唔想再受傷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上大量文宣鋪天蓋地cover<br />\n除非外國人自私到仆街，唔係實合可憐你<br />\n<br />\n可以喺機場話I am sorry for any inconvenience. Please contact your country's embassy for protection NOW. It helps you as well as exerting pressure on HKGOV.<br />\n<br />\n呢啲時候M文宣就好重要，首先我地要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.清晰五大訴求嘅slogan，等遊客知我地發生咩事</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2.打多啲同情牌，必要時之前跪住叫人擺工嘅方法可以再用，表面功夫要做足，我地係比香港政府逼到絕路先阻到你</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3.人多！！！講幾多嘢都無用，無人實收皮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣明面上打同情牌，暗地鍊住政府春袋，就可以出師有名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且用同理心，機場人多無wifi，好多旅客除咗白等係唔知應該點做的，想上網search點做都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候最需係指引遊客可以點做，例如租酒店，claim保險，附近邊度有酒店，搵航班同AA投訴或者claim錢，總之將個問題帶比政府機構，避免示威者同遊客對立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣達至最大效益？當然係將呢啲資訊同文宣夾埋一齊整成小册子，大家都想要呢本嘢，令香港情況更易輸出，亦都做返示威者友善一面比國際睇，拎返民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會建議小冊子有以下內容<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.點解要反送中<br />\n2.五大訴求<br />\n3.示威者被逼壓，被傷害嘅圖，每頁有埋Qr code可以睇埋相關濫權合集<br />\n4.道歉！阻到你唔好意思，但呢度係唯一唔洗比狗射嘅地方<br />\n5.有資料點求助，將個波推比政府</span><br />\n<br />\n咁文宣黎講要超級M，將和理非嘅作用放到最大，亦都係和理非可以cover勇武手足嘅機合！"},{"pid":"693e9f3fe63b124ea252b3400b6487dc05c693ad","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"e32815cdbb83c65b0b5df500a4a23184aeb2a7d0","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"820cf260b0bf45eba49bc63d410902afcc4d76b4","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:13:04.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1c37a782e00e53aed69067c1fce557ad94dcb51b","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ac236f98071a5526fa9737b32b565d0f234b0ee8","tid":1463970,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f842ab8a6991fb2ab321bee379d3241e55bf7f7d","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n<br />\n同狗一樣，佢地幾仆街都好，只要每日記招門面功夫做足，一樣大把藍絲信<br />\n和理非咁擅長門面嘢做弱者，呢個位唔可以輸！"},{"pid":"87bd47758592704e69cb1afa9633766d9eede675","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:57.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb39b7a607915e8897a17c90e0d37163f9719e9","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"49432d6be08ac4f7e1699903eefc7c4e69a745bb","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"cee0069aeb10194732a3738d2a3e61069b7f272c","tid":1463970,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"5f80e5b4106be6dc618a79f28f5db7c476e223c7","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:32.000Z","msg":"唔好捉鬼吊人<br />\n快啲take action贏返之後幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8"},{"pid":"023139c4d8d065cc1f3b0da13ad292580fb414fd","tid":1463970,"uid":50791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee0069aeb10194732a3738d2a3e61069b7f272c","tid":1463970,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"塞，但都要道歉<br />\n我係m男，阻到你唔好意思，求你鞭打本王，扣本王50分，唔好比人同本王擦背"},{"pid":"03a79599cb687451c56